END_PGML
############################################################ # Hint ############################################################ #Set value of $showHint in PGcourse.pl for course-wide attempt threshhold for revealing hints
BEGIN_PGML_HINT Re-write each of the trigonometric functions in terms of [`\sin x`] and [`\cos x\text{,}`] then simplify. Remember that your final answer should not use any of the other trigonometric functions, only [`\sin x`] and/or [`\cos x\text{.}`]
END_PGML_HINT
